comments: Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bayless (MIN) and does not deliver contact.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thompson (GSW) and does not deliver contact.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal contact to the arm of Towns (MIN) during the drive and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Durant (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bayless (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Wiggins (MIN) makes marginal contact to the arm of Durant (GSW) during the drive and the contact does not affect his SQBR.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Durant (GSW) dribbles the ball out of bounds.
Thompson (GSW) briefly places two hands on Towns (MIN) in the post, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to establish position.
Green (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bayless (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball when he deflects it away from Towns (MIN).  Following the contact with the ball, Green briefly engages with Towns and immediately releases.
Wiggins (MIN) makes marginal contact to the body of Durant (GSW) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Both Thompson (GSW) and Green (GSW) make clean contact with the ball and Green steals it from Wiggins (MIN).
Wiggins (MIN) makes contact to Green's (GSW) arm after the steal that affects his SQBR.
Green (GSW) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage off ball.
Durant (GSW) makes incidental contact to the arm of Wiggins (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Tolliver (MIN) and Iguodala (GSW) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reynolds (MIN) and does not deliver contact.
Towns (MIN) makes contact to the body of Durant (GSW) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bayless (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Durant (GSW) grabs Towns (MIN) and restricts his FOM.
Durant (GSW) makes marginal contact with Towns (MIN) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
LLB shows Durant (GSW) makes contact to the body of Towns (MIN) during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Bayless (MIN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Durant's (GSW) possession during his drive to the basket.  Durant and Okogie (MIN) make incidental contact with each other while the ball is loose.
Iguodala (GSW) briefly grasps Towns' (MIN) arm during the screen but does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Iguodala (GSW) makes marginal contact with Tolliver (MIN) at the start of the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Tolliver (MIN) and Iguodala (GSW) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Durant (GSW) and does not deliver contact.
RLB shows Thompson (GSW) makes contact to the body of Okogie (MIN) during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Okogie (MIN) makes marginal "hot-stove" contact with Curry's (GSW) leg after the release of his jump shot attempt and does not affect his ability to land safely.
Curry (GSW) commits a take foul on Bayless (MIN).
Thompson (GSW) commits a take foul on Okogie (MIN).
Bates-Diop (MIN) places two hands on Durant (GSW) and makes contact with him prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Curry (GSW) makes incidental contact with Bayless (MIN) during his jump shot attempt but does not affect Bayless' ability to contest.
Durant (GSW) wraps Towns (MIN) around the waist and engages with him, restricting his FOM.  The path of the throw-in has no bearing on the illegal action.
